明白了，以下是一个更强调**“价值导向”**而非纯技术细节的版本，突出你为团队和项目带来的影响和成果：


---

"Focused on delivering long-term value by aligning test strategies with project goals at each phase. Drove improvements in processes and tools not just for efficiency, but to enable faster feedback, better risk visibility, and higher confidence in releases. Through continuous collaboration and iteration, helped the team achieve more reliable outcomes and build a scalable testing foundation for future projects."


---

这个版本弱化了技术术语，强化了贡献的影响、目标导向和业务价值。如需突出某个“成效指标”或“影响范围”，可以再加一句。需要吗？

